## Limitations

This report is based on available literature and may not cover all possible reasons for startup failure. The data is subject to the limitations of the studies and articles referenced, which may not account for all industry-specific challenges or recent market changes. Additionally, the failure reasons are often interconnected, making it difficult to isolate a single cause.